Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its body is armoured\Nin iron and concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its mind is wrapped in\Ncomputers and high technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the city and\Nthe time we're living in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most people ignore\Nthe unexplainable or mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things that we can't\Ndecipher through ordinary logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around these ordinary people,\Nfollowing common rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the while seeking out\Nstrong desires and pleasures...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hanging on to\Na little happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there exists a vast and fearful world\Nof darkness beyond our time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}I'm afraid I know all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost the bet, so I have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just guessed wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.91,0:01:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I've been a\Nbartender for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a girl who has kept\Nher guard up as much as Kanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have imagined\Nthat she'd accept your offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck! I'll keep this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's certainly taking her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she comes. 10,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean 10,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.79,0:02:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's none of your business.\NIs it Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be so secretive.\NAlright, I'll find out tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long Ken. Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.\NSee you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taki, why don't we bet on\Nthe Giants and Tigers game, next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A re-match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I was happy.\NLike I fell into rapture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the girl that I liked, at the\Nbar I frequently visited for 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, she asked me\Nto come to her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a surprise.\NWhat made you change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live in this luxurious place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a little too bold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like impatient girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I am more of\Na romantic than I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so strong.\NI'm so attracted to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This woman has a devil inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She completely changed\Nfrom how she was at the bar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was very different than what I'd\Nexpected, but I'm not complaining.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You realised a little too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're of no use to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll relieve you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.\NI've already got what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to Kanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so worried about the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made her sleep in\Nthe restroom, at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's not much time before\Nthe signing of the peace treaty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WICKED CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right... yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir, I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you very much.\NI'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taki, the President\Nwants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess your playboy lifestyle\Nhas caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your concern.\NIt pierced my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taki, you want to join us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mah-jong? Sounds good!\NBut I'm completely broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better look for another sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no bigger sucker than you.\NSee ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all the suckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Renzaburo Taki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I work at the sales department of an\Nelectronics company in Shibuya, Tokyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my official job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taki from the\Nsales department is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a MacGregor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I finally got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grip and hit are really nice.\NIt's perfect, just what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.09,0:07:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I heard you\Nhad a strange experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't trust\Nthe peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it those extremists?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so... but for now, I filed\Na complaint with their leaders...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the Vatican.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd better be careful\Nwhich women you date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your biggest weakness is women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any reason for them to\Nbe taking action now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The signing ceremony date for the next\Npeace treaty has been moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be held tomorrow, in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Investigations have discovered that\Npeople from the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have illegally infiltrated this side\Nby using a shield breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must take care of this quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt, that when this\Npeace treaty is signed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will start a new era in the\Nrelationship between both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The terms of this treaty will maintain\Nthe peace for another 500 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, a V.I.P. is arriving at Narita airport, 7 p.m. tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's attending the signing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to guard him\Nuntil tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Black Guard,\NMr. Renzaburo Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Black Guard,\Nthat's my other face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your life is always\Nin danger with that job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's finally coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't close the\Npeace treaty without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please guard him closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be the main target of the\Nextremists who are against this treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for giving me\Nsuch a thoughtful assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to assign you a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her skills are the very best and\NI hear she's good looking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be waiting for\Nyou at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for the best\Nlooking woman there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.\NShe's from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Guard from\Nthe other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so don't get any\Nstrange ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I know,\Nmore than anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how scary the women are\Nfrom the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is the world where humans live,\Nand then there's another world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the demon world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've been in contact with\Neach other throughout our histories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two worlds have sought interaction,\Nharmony, and coexistence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, there have been fierce and bitter battles...\Nfought between our worlds, again and again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, the heads of our two worlds\Nmade a treaty for coexistence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a kind of a secret deal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truce is renewed\Nevery couple of hundred years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now, as we approach\Nthe end of the twentieth century,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these two worlds are trying\Nto close the new peace treaty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't resolve this\Nwith friendly conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that toy\Nwill work on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, this toy\Nisn't what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't look\Ngood in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're my partner.\NYou saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For such a skilled guard,\Nyou're still quite a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm much obliged by\Nyour honest opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renzaburo Taki, 25 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Height 180 cm, weight 65 kg,\Nblood type AB.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Official job is a salesman of\Nan electronics company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monthly salary is 230,000 yen.\NSingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you? Don't forget to include\Nyour measurements, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Makie, no last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job on this side is as a model.\NBut I've got no reputation in that job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sponsors don't like me because\NI scared off all the other models.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Your beauty is too perfect.\NIt's almost unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have to hurry.\NHe will be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dedication to the job\Nis such a sad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person\Nwill we be guarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A traditional demon emissary\Nand a great medium...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he had retired and was\Nliving in the ruins of Pompeii,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or at the heart of the Apollonian Mountains,\Nafter he attended the signing ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the last treaty in 1851.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he's the key person\Nfor the signing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I hope everything goes smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did they choose\Nyou as my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you must have great skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you don't trust\Nwomen from the demon world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost never.\NI've had a very bad experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This partnership is not\Nwhat I wanted either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just follow my superior's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. We have to stick\Ntogether until this assignment ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! They really did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much to do,\Njust to kill one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had sensed danger,\Nso I moved up to an earlier flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Giuseppe Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to be with the\Ntwo of you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was told that a woman from\Nthe other side would be guarding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're much more\Nbeautiful than I had expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rude!\NWhat did you just do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the rude one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!\NThis is a greeting in the human world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart, I think it's good\Nthat you're so lively,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have to be a little discreet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's\Njust for tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she and I have been\Nassigned to protect your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything you want after\Nthe treaty is signed tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but until then, I want you\Nto follow our rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? She's just a\Nwoman of the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what kind of real form\Nshe has under that beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must already know what happens\Nto the people who sleep with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all became zombies after their\Nlife energies were sucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why so many people\Nstill want to have sex with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People feel such incredible ecstasy,\Nit can't even compare with human sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful too, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch your tongue, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel confident\Nprotecting you by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about that.\NA job is a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect anyone,\Neven at the risk of my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those words make me feel\Nreally secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I leave the matter\Nto both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure that\Nno danger comes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I still want to taste this\Nspecial ecstasy at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special hotel built\Nwith an energy barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to shield us from the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was made for the safety\Nof a special V.I.P., like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place seems boring.\NI came all the way to Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't I visit some hostess club\Nor a massage parlour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a musty smell in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.\NI'm the owner of this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be exhausted after\Nsuch a long trip to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, our hotel\Nis not luxurious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...please hold out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will provide the\Nbest service we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.\NAre you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've heard you\Nare doing well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the guest\Narrangements today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,\Nit's just you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a big terrorist group on\Nthe other side wants to destroy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be careful, even if this\Narea is protected from invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier's resistance level has\Nbeen increased by three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pushing me to take him out\Nand have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taki.\NThis woman is so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.77,0:22:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.\NMassage Parlour Playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They provide so many good\Nlooking women. Let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... you don't like that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?\NCabaret Club Queen Mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the place for us!\NLet's go to this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go with you wherever\Nyou want, after this assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you. You're so picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this!?\NAnd don't complain anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fashion Massage Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.13,0:23:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot give you permission\Nto go outside of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.68,0:23:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. You're stubborn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will sleep with us\Nin this room, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I certainly object.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep with that woman,\Nbut never with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep with a\Nman being next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.26,0:23:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you don't have to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This peace treaty can't\Nconclude without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of this, you still trap\Nme in such a crappy hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hotel is located above the\Npoint where the most powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spiritual energy can\Nbe transmitted in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way for them to enter.\NThey can't even come close.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why is that woman here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a member of the\NBlack Guard from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has been trained\Nfor this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if I can be alone with her,\NI'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sleep in the hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.39,0:24:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll stay with you Mr. Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.13,0:24:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance to try a\Nwoman of the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.28,0:24:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he does something strange,\Njust tie him to the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you telling her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.62,0:24:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nincompoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guest upstairs is a\Ntruly important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.78,0:25:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.17,0:25:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe Mayart...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to Japan,\Nincognito, 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.44,0:25:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't changed much\Nsince then, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder a little,\Nif he's for real or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.55,0:25:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just my intuition,\Nbut in my humble opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.36,0:25:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he might be a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.93,0:25:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They use a decoy freely, to attract\Nthe enemy's attention to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.67,0:25:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.91,0:25:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you still single?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.41,0:25:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by\Njust looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.81,0:25:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the lady\Nyou came with?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke. She's a woman\Nfrom the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have children,\Nbut I hear the sex is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.72,0:25:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never thought I would hear\Nsuch words coming from your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.93,0:26:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?\NIt's just what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.59,0:26:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.87,0:26:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.89,0:26:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be proud of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.83,0:26:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very honourable to have such an\Nimportant job, protecting both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.89,0:26:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it? I don't know if it's worth\Nprotecting human or demon society,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.61,0:26:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by risking my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.49,0:26:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you still don't\Nhave anything to truly protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.83,0:26:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better find something fast,\Nthen you'll understand its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.11,0:26:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to protect?\NIs it that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.73,0:26:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.94,0:26:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,973)}Checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.65,0:26:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let's have one more game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.87,0:26:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you never give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.27,0:26:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain!\NI'm helping you kill time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.95,0:27:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.56,0:27:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! They're trying\Nto break the spiritual shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.92,0:27:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... there's no way\Nfor them to enter here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.56,0:27:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.83,0:28:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart, don't leave there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.45,0:28:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.92,0:28:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.71,0:29:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look nice, wearing\Nthe clothes of this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.78,0:29:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've joined hand\Nin hand with the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.58,0:29:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.34,0:29:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you betray us?\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.10,0:29:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are such lowly\Ncreatures compared to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will just have to serve us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to be equal or fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.70,0:29:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want you\Nto understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.71,0:29:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as stubborn\Nas you used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.92,0:29:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have made you\Nsleep with me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.66,0:30:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can take\Nmy heart, if you take my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.91,0:30:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the way you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.95,0:30:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try?\NI'll make you crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.79,0:30:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.61,0:30:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they only got my\Nfake hand. You should go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.77,0:31:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? Your body is\Nmore honest than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.89,0:31:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.79,0:31:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.\NYou can't use that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.52,0:31:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.20,0:31:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.46,0:31:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mr. Mayart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.67,0:31:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hiding in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.38,0:32:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,853)}What kind of emissary is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.22,0:32:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Taki. I relied on this\Nspiritual barrier wall too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.96,0:32:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you find Mr. Mayart?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.54,0:32:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I have an\Nidea where he's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.84,0:32:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is paradise. I could never\Nimagine such a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I've lived long\Nenough to experience this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.01,0:32:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting so full of energy,\Nbecause you are so pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.57,0:32:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the full treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, why don't you lie\Ndown on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.65,0:32:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.83,0:32:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sir, you have so much vitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.01,0:32:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can even outlast young men.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.99,0:32:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.36,0:32:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living so long,\NI don't remember anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.78,0:32:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am well past 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.68,0:33:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Nobody your age\Ncan keep it up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.32,0:33:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have both had a very long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.97,0:33:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, you have marvellous breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.07,0:33:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're like art that God created.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.73,0:33:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you look like a baby doing that.\NYou don't look 200 years old at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.17,0:33:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.77,0:33:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swallowed something.\NWhat was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI haven't had a baby yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.21,0:33:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.09,0:33:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.16,0:33:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paradise, paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.70,0:33:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...\NWhat the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.67,0:33:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take you to the\Nreal Paradise, Giuseppe Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.16,0:34:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a terrorist from\Nthe demon world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.06,0:34:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayart...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.95,0:34:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill me, the old man dies too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.86,0:34:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.74,0:34:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki, rescue Mr. Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.83,0:34:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of your lives will end tonight,\Nno matter how far you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.06,0:34:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one whose life will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.07,0:35:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.\NHis life force is almost drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.60,0:35:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to give him\Nspiritual treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.81,0:35:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.07,0:35:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spiritual treatment hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.55,0:35:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take one hour\Nno matter how fast I drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.73,0:35:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, hope he can hold out until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.73,0:35:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reaction to\Nmy psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not last\Nmore than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.68,0:35:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's caused a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.10,0:35:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.55,0:35:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are trying to take us\Ninto demon space.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.53,0:35:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.14,0:36:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been transported\Ninto demon space.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.59,0:36:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car.\NIt's no use driving anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.26,0:36:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.15,0:36:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here with Mr. Mayart.\NI will break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.54,0:36:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.56,0:36:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I'm willing to risk\Nmy life for this assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.31,0:36:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't heard your\Nmeasurements yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.55,0:36:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.98,0:37:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! That soap girl was a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.30,0:37:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.51,0:38:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.17,0:38:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki... run away, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.34,0:38:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect Mr. Mayart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.38,0:38:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon space barrier\Nis about to open.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.33,0:38:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry... hurry up and run...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.96,0:39:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.33,0:40:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're in Motoakasaka...\NStill far away from the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.12,0:40:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Makie is gone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.29,0:40:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She used up all her energy and power to\Nbreak through the demon space barrier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.65,0:40:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She might have been blown up\Nwhen the barrier was broken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.54,0:40:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She helped us by sacrificing herself.\NA woman from the demon world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.13,0:40:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope she's still alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.98,0:41:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(61,81,806.2,81)\an2}SPIRITUAL TREATMENT CENTRE
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.23,0:41:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.80,0:41:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His life force is incredible. I think\Nhe'll recover in less than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.36,0:41:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make sure this place\Nhas enough protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.41,0:41:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spiritual barrier here is\N20 times stronger than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.73,0:41:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different from\Nthe Teito Hotel in Hibiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.84,0:41:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been fighting with them for\N5,000 years. We've learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.48,0:41:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.72,0:41:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.87,0:41:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.72,0:41:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! We're completely\Nsurrounded by a demon space barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.42,0:41:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a radius of 5 kilometres!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.38,0:41:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Increase the barrier's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.40,0:42:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a request for help to\NIndia, Tibet, and Mt. Koya...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.50,0:42:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to strengthen the spiritual wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.49,0:42:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart, you still\Nhave a lot to go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.59,0:42:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me,\NRenzaburo Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.06,0:42:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something interesting\Nto show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.34,0:42:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.26,0:43:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.31,0:43:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this well.\NThis is the end of a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.57,0:43:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a resident of the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.07,0:43:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite that, she assisted\Nthis deceptive peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.06,0:43:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, she's killed her ex-lover.\NThere is no way to forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.64,0:43:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will let her serve the\Ndesires of these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.62,0:43:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I will torture her slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.97,0:43:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taki, don't you want\Nto rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.12,0:43:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.67,0:43:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of that?\NWhy don't you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.09,0:43:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.21,0:43:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.26,0:43:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! This is a trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they have clearly\Nchallenged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.67,0:43:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.55,0:43:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think\Nwill happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.33,0:44:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Black Guard,\Nyou're supposed to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.76,0:44:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you stay here,\Nthey can't even touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.10,0:44:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.34,0:44:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Important enough to go and\Nsave her, by leaving me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.35,0:44:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget! She's a woman\Nof the demon world!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.45,0:44:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.77,0:44:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sacrificed herself to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.83,0:44:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she should!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.08,0:44:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an irreplaceable\NDemon Emissary in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.23,0:44:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peace treaty of the two worlds\Ncan't be signed without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.92,0:44:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even compare me\Nwith that monster bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.11,0:44:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She deserves to be raped and\Ntortured by her fellow monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.14,0:44:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might even be enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.92,0:45:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge.\NLet me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.51,0:45:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.\NI will guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.51,0:45:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... what did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.41,0:45:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You would leave me here?\NI haven't given you permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.48,0:45:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you know\Nwhat you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.64,0:45:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a professional Black Guard,\Nyou're acting ridiculously!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.68,0:45:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.76,0:45:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.55,0:46:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Guard, Renzaburo Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.14,0:46:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sworn enemy has\Nfallen into our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.97,0:46:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think that\NI'll let you die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.60,0:46:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman... let Makie go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.28,0:46:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in love with her?\NDo you want to sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.20,0:46:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't express your\Nown dirty thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.21,0:46:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.54,0:47:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will test your ability\Nas a man, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.03,0:47:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask your body how\Nmuch you're involved...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with this disgusting\Nconspiracy that's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.56,0:47:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.90,0:48:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me. Inside my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.21,0:48:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No man can resist this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.59,0:48:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.00,0:48:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will suck everything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.46,0:48:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.33,0:48:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.80,0:48:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?\NIncredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.94,0:48:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will do anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.70,0:49:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about the\Nconspiracy on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.61,0:49:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman... Makie.\NDid you sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.35,0:49:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.71,0:49:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.33,0:49:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.28,0:49:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the prince who came\Nhere to save the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.61,0:49:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fantasy ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.58,0:50:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assimilation seems\Nlike it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.19,0:50:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.54,0:50:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what has just happened\Nto the men you beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.69,0:51:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!\NShoot as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.34,0:51:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Renzaburo Taki,\Nthis is your end.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.29,0:52:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!\NHow come you have so much power?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.85,0:53:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.91,0:53:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.45,0:53:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a deep wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.93,0:53:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.90,0:53:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that you would\Nhave come here to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.77,0:53:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my partner.\NOf course I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.14,0:53:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became the enemy's hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.83,0:53:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned your post,\Nright in the middle of an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.10,0:53:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll both be fired\Nfrom the Black Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.32,0:53:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something\Nthat worries me more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.88,0:53:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this conspiracy they\Nwere asking me about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.84,0:53:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did they want to know\Nif I slept with Makie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.09,0:53:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there a secret\Nconspiracy going on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.46,0:53:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}behind the peace treaty\Nbeing signed tomorrow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.68,0:54:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the man who came to\Nthe hotel, your ex-boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.47,0:54:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.77,0:54:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He completely changed after being\Nbrainwashed by the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.66,0:54:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a nice person before.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.06,0:54:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice but to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.39,0:54:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NThat's the way our job goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.97,0:54:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you become a Black Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.62,0:54:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people\Nwho want peace in both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.91,0:54:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both worlds need to coexist\Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.38,0:54:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that to happen,\Nsomebody has to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.37,0:54:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mr. Mayart well?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.17,0:54:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being protected at\Nthe spiritual hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.43,0:54:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to pick him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.81,0:54:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.50,0:54:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your psychic powers have\Nhealed me well. I'm already cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.30,0:54:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you'll get cold\Ndressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.30,0:55:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.31,0:55:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.32,0:55:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can imagine that you\Nwere working as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.93,0:55:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me before,\NI have unreal beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.14,0:55:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel that way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.13,0:55:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have perfect beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.07,0:55:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.36,0:55:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.25,0:56:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already acting like\Nboyfriend and girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.55,0:56:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must've had\Nlots of fun, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.21,0:56:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is supposed to\Nbe guarding Mr. Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.74,0:56:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you walk away from it,\Njust to do the things you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.28,0:56:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have disgraced me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.08,0:56:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so happy-go-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.98,0:56:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've went to a love hotel\Nand made out. You rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.34,0:56:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are already dismissed.\NPlease leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.49,0:56:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will send you\Na formal notice, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.73,0:56:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! I'll have nothing to do with\Nincompetent people like you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.48,0:56:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.49,0:56:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.57,0:56:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.18,0:56:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a lot of potential to\Nbecome a great Black Guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.59,0:56:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're too much of a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.19,0:57:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your biggest flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you?\NI've made a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.98,0:57:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.11,0:57:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I should have\Nfinished him off, that last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.12,0:57:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only survivors.\NThere's no time to call for backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.55,0:57:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and finish him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.06,0:57:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I got the result of his\Nbody fluid analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.39,0:57:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.90,0:57:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the DNA?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.92,0:57:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.51,0:58:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take a while for me\Nto regenerate. You take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.52,0:58:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1056)}I will take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.90,0:58:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.59,0:58:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.\NIt's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.97,0:58:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did everything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.43,0:58:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a romantic\Nisn't right for this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.71,0:58:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.\NEspecially not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.14,0:59:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am quite a romantic myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.68,0:59:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you follow us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.13,0:59:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are no sexy nurses\Nin that hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.10,1:00:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are rough men.\NIt felt so stuffy being there.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.02,1:00:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't a good excuse!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.91,1:00:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Can we go to a place\Ncalled "Cabaret Club" next?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.67,1:00:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.02,1:00:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got fired from being\Nyour babysitter!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.53,1:00:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.81,1:00:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just do what I want to do,\Nand I'll take all the blame for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.05,1:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayart, don't you realise,\Nyou have a very important job?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.22,1:00:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!\NI certainly know that!!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.21,1:00:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have a\Nlittle time, until then.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.48,1:00:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.93,1:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you back\Nto the Teito Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.14,1:00:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much closer than taking\Nyou back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.61,1:00:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Do that!\NI can escape from there at any time.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.11,1:00:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.42,1:01:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.69,1:01:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.89,1:01:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.28,1:01:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.65,1:02:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.39,1:02:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.80,1:02:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.54,1:02:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,355)}How could you fall\Nin love with a human?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.14,1:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who love each other\Ncan die together.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.66,1:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an envious ending!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.42,1:02:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chop up both of\Nyour cursed bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.78,1:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.10,1:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.89,1:06:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a dream?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.14,1:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a dream,\NI don't want it to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.91,1:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.19,1:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.33,1:06:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, who live in the demon world,\Nshouldn't have tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.30,1:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have\Ntears inside of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.54,1:06:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened...\NI guess we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.58,1:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who brought us here?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.53,1:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe God.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.03,1:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to think that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.82,1:07:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.\NThey're very close.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.12,1:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuseppe Mayart!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.69,1:08:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NThe enemy is behind you!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.23,1:08:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect! I've finally encountered\Nmy real enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.65,1:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have to hurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.02,1:08:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go? Where should we go to?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.22,1:08:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the signing ceremony of\Nthe peace treaty, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.06,1:08:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where you should go!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.53,1:08:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are the ones who must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.53,1:08:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.07,1:08:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't realise it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.05,1:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you two\Nwho were guarding me.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.57,1:08:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was called here\Nto guard you two.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.60,1:09:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was you who carried\Nus here and healed us?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.66,1:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I used my psychic powers\Nto heal both of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.04,1:09:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.38,1:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.06,1:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure a lasting peace,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.79,1:09:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we felt that some kind of\Nspiritual exchange was needed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.55,1:09:22.67,Default,,0005,0005,0000,,{\fs38}Something representing the spiritual wave between the human world and the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.89,1:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the biggest barrier that kept\Nour two worlds from interacting,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.57,1:09:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that there's no way to mix\Nthe blood of each other's race.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.49,1:09:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, after a few thousand\Nyears of our effort,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.30,1:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some spiritual mutation had occurred.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.47,1:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still very few, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.78,1:09:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we've produced some subjects whose\NDNA can be mixed with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.17,1:09:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the scientists of both worlds\Nselected the best couple.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.31,1:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Makie are the first couple.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.24,1:10:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can have a child who bears\Nthe gifts from both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.18,1:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's that child who will\Nbecome the leader of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.55,1:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.84,1:10:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...child?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.11,1:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.19,1:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These terrorists are afraid of that,\Nand have tried to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.86,1:10:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You doddering old fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.11,1:10:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much more\Nwill you interfere with us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.21,1:10:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you. Still alive?\NWhat are you made of?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.13,1:10:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both should have taken\Neach other more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.46,1:10:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring this to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.41,1:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and eat him up\Nuntil he's just bones!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.09,1:11:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our power is far beyond\Nany human's ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.82,1:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.33,1:12:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!!!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.27,1:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.74,1:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ye-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.63,1:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used too much power.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.10,1:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still trying to regenerate?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess rapidly regenerating in his\Ncondition must have some side effects.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.19,1:13:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.09,1:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece of meat will\Njust keep on regenerating.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.77,1:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.89,1:14:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and fight me!\NI'll turn you into a puff of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.54,1:14:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.92,1:14:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she...?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.52,1:15:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.78,1:15:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the effect of the mutation.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.39,1:15:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has definitely conceived.\NThis power is the best proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.65,1:15:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makie is already pregnant,\Nwith your baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.87,1:15:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never imagined the symptoms\Nwould come so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.86,1:16:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one condition needed in\Norder for Makie to conceive a baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.59,1:16:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The laboratory concluded that in order\Nto conceive and transfigure the DNA,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.44,1:16:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the couple had to have\Na spiritual bond of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.76,1:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I made you go\Nthrough all this effort.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.00,1:16:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to bring out\Nyour love for each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.61,1:16:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.89,1:16:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no other way,\Nunder such a tight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.99,1:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.02,1:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.78,1:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was planned ahead?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.39,1:16:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.98,1:16:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, nobody could predict if the\Ntwo of you could love each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.53,1:16:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like beating you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.17,1:16:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you serious when\Nyou made love to Makie?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.16,1:16:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.36,1:16:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.82,1:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.69,1:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at first.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.45,1:17:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.06,1:17:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe a woman\Nof the demon world?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.87,1:17:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears you had.\NI believe they were real.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.63,1:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... the results have\Nexceeded our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.93,1:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, Taki won't beat me up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.53,1:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.90,1:17:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new treaty, the start of\Na new life, and a new world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.84,1:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite a character.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.67,1:18:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The long night ends.\NA bright day breaks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.77,1:18:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like the man at\Nthe hotel told me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.78,1:18:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone whom I should protect\Nis in my arms, right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.80,1:18:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there is my child...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.11,1:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who doesn't even have shape,\Nbut is inside of her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.14,1:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This child may create a new future\Nfor both worlds, someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.25,1:19:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.47,1:19:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my job...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.97,1:19:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as a Black Guard won't end,\Nuntil that day comes.{\i0}
